{"tid":1291984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私家車在尖沙咀疑失控衝上行人路　初步知道十人傷","createTime":"2019-07-07T06:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:17:20.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e48d8349e6dfd190c48ccd8b9fbf81cbee30b2","tid":1291984,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀下午發生交通意外，初步知道有十人受傷，其中一人昏迷送院。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午約一時半，一輛私家車駛至金馬倫道與漆咸道南交界時，懷疑失控衝上行人路，撞向一間商舖，造成多人受傷，包括私家車司機，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66325023_1151547438370656_322005724089548800_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQlzqoPSHCvuP8ojp3NIZX5YxD8M1Nsr0WZCRFup6YE1O7M0p-ZySJC-Y7L_pjz5s7w&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=74934f9331d2e276382ecc7f5b9496e8&amp;oe=5DAFA45E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66325023_1151547438370656_322005724089548800_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQlzqoPSHCvuP8ojp3NIZX5YxD8M1Nsr0WZCRFup6YE1O7M0p-ZySJC-Y7L_pjz5s7w%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D74934f9331d2e276382ecc7f5b9496e8%26oe%3D5DAFA45E&h=a110c25f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30af83aaa780130b84290f21ef6f9b31173c0e78","tid":1291984,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66432343_3061514277222392_84494462117478400_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQnJrZbv6SxKpeYRb0DCg1ToXm5t6-pl86MHYj-XCQNfcZGgz7J6YRloLNF_7TlLjPg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=2772c92c10f4b71c3c852dcd2565f53b&amp;oe=5DA9FA0A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66432343_3061514277222392_84494462117478400_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQnJrZbv6SxKpeYRb0DCg1ToXm5t6-pl86MHYj-XCQNfcZGgz7J6YRloLNF_7TlLjPg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D2772c92c10f4b71c3c852dcd2565f53b%26oe%3D5DA9FA0A&h=3f8e0c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}